sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
    participant spa
    
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: HTML document for SPA
    deactivate server
    
    Note right of browser: The browser loads the SPA HTML document
    
    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.js
    activate server
    server-->>browser: the JavaScript file
    deactivate server
    
    Note right of browser: The browser loads the JavaScript file for the SPA
    
    browser->>spa: User interacts with the Single Page App
    
    Note right of spa: The SPA handles user interactions without page reloads
    
    spa->>server: API requests to fetch data
    activate server
    server-->>spa: JSON data for the SPA
    deactivate server
    
    Note right of spa: The SPA fetches data from the server using API calls
    
    spa->>browser: Updating the UI with new data
    Note right of browser: The SPA updates the UI dynamically without full page reloads
    
    browser->>spa: User continues interacting with the SPA
